Package main.models

Class MovieGoer

java.lang.Object
main.models.MovieGoer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MovieGoer extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a Movie-goer who has purchased movie ticket(s). A movie-goer can reuse the stored card number for future payments. All payments are stored as transactions.

  • Constructor Details

    • MovieGoer

      public MovieGoer(String name, String mobile, String email, String cardNumber)
      Creates a new movie-goer with the given fields when the user makes a booking for the first time. None of the fields should be empty. The mobile number must be 8 to 15 digits long. The card number must be 8 to 19 digits long.
      Parameters:
      name - name of movie-goer
      mobile - mobile number of movie-goer
      email - email address of movie-goer
      cardNumber - card number of movie-goer
